{"tid":439951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]  下 周一「霜 降」  最 低 溫 2 0 °C　！！","createTime":"2017-10-18T09:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T05:01:30.000Z","uid":82845,"like":146,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7b26f2f2894e16aaa9e7a315f0f4d699b645ea","tid":439951,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171018/57346665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171018%2F57346665&d=oxF5rSRworSiBm66GbGd8P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c711b2e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171018%2F57346665&h=0a186e8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171018/57346665</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171018/large/1508304141_ff58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171018%2Flarge%2F1508304141_ff58.jpg&h=a36a023d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日星期三，天晴陽光充沛。天文台最新9天天氣預報顯示，乾燥的東北季候風會在未來數天及下週為華南帶來晴朗的天氣，日夜溫差較大。下週初廣東沿岸地區天氣稍涼，周一最低溫預料20&deg;C。天氣乾燥，涼涼哋，周未行山BBQ，最正啦！<br />\n<br />\n無獨有偶，下周一(23日)正是二十四節氣中第十八個節氣--霜降。霜降是秋天最後的一個節氣，太陽到達黃經210&deg;，指暑氣慢慢消退，在夜晚和早晨，地面水蒸汽遇冷就凝結成露珠，如果遇到更冷的空氣就會結霜，通常在每年西曆的10月23日或24日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07285913e3d013a1ba3a6e068b063dd966c95e2c","tid":439951,"uid":13504,"like":665,"dislike":10,"scor